headline: Citigroup taps Adam Inzirillo from Cboe for equities business
summary: In his new role, Inzirillo will oversee Citi’s electronic execution platform, focusing on trading algorithms and direct market access offerings, the person said.  He will join in October as global head of the execution platform for the equities business and report to Sebastien Mailleux, global co-head of prime services, the person added.
